# APIDriftRadar - Latency Drift and Status Monitor

APIDriftRadar helps spot slowdowns, spikes, and unstable API trends before outages happen.

## Features
- Real-time response tracking  
- Drift alert system  
- JSON / CSV export  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/34_APIDriftRadar.git
cd 34_APIDriftRadar
python monitor.py
